      "content": "Combining melatonin and zolpidem is not something you should do without consulting your doctor. Melatonin and zolpidem work in different ways, and mixing them could potentially lead to excessive drowsiness or other side effects. It is best to discuss your sleep difficulties and any concerns about medication interactions with your healthcare provider. They can help you find a safe and effective treatment plan for your insomnia.",
